outline of a deal which ideally would force Serbian President
Slobodan Milosevic to his knees.
</P>
<P>
   Late on Friday night, an errant NATO missile scored its most
devastating target imaginable _ a direct hit on the Chinese embassy
in Belgrade.
</P>
<P>
   At a stroke the painstaking feat of the diplomats had been at
the least imperiled, conceivably reduced to as much rubble as
China's mission... &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; (NOTE: Article can stand in 625; total uncut version is 1,100
words.) &LR;  &QC;
</P>
