regulations for body piercing and tanning salons, pollution and
other bills. By JOHN GONZALEZ.
</P>
<P>
   ALCOHOL-TEXAS (Austin, Texas) _ We look at the alcohol-related
legislation approved in a flurry of activity in the Texas House on
Tuesday, including a bill on open containers. By JOHN GONZALEZ.
</P>
