   BKN-ROCKETS (Houston) _ Reeling in the wake of two straight
losses and internal disputes, the Houston Rockets return home
facing elimination in their best-of-five NBA playoff series against
the Los Angeles Lakers. By JONATHAN FEIGEN.
</P>
