   KOSOVO-PILOT _ RINAS AIR FIELD, Albania _ ``A Day In The Live of
An Apache Pilot.'' We follow the nonclassified parts of the routine
of an Apache pilot named Matt, who is from Michigan and a member of
the West Point Class of 1996. He talks about his feelings about his
two lost comrades, who were his friends and lived in a tent near
his. (Albright, Cox News Service). 30. WITH PHOTOS.
