   RUBIN _ WASHINGTON _ President Clinton will announce Wednesday
afternoon that Treasury Secretary Robert Rubin was leaving the
administration and that he was nominating Rubin's deputy, Lawrence
Summers, to replace him. (Deans, Cox News Service). 25.
