confirmed _ that Treasury Secretary Robert Rubin is resigning,
knocked the Dow down almost 200 points. It was a sign of how much
Wall Street likes Rubin. How will Wall Street take to his apparent
successor, Lawrence Summers? (McNaughton, Cox News Service). 20.
