</P>
<P>
   (NYT21) CEGRANE, Macedonia -- May 12, 1999 --
KOSOVO-REFUGEES-FLOATER-1, 5-12 -- German army soldiers throw candy
to young ethnic Albanian refugees at a refugee camp on Wednesday.
(Tyler Hicks/New York Times Photo)
</P>
