<P>
   COUPLE-DIE (Seattle) _ Gladys and Pete Saccomanno met in a
Harley-Davidson shop in Colorado, and spent the next 57 years
riding motorcycles, bowling and betting on horse races together.
Friday night, paramedics took Pete _ struck with lymphoma cancer _
to the hospital, and Gladys knew he wasn't coming back. They died
within minutes of each other, he in the hospital and she in the
ambulance on her way there after an apparent stroke.
