NEW YORK TIMES CORRECTIONS FOR THURSDAY, MAY 13
</HEADLINE>
 Eds.: These corrections will appear in The New York Times on
Thursday. Days and dates refer to the original article's
transmission by the New York Times News Service, and may need to be
adjusted by NYT clients.)  
(gc) 
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   BC-LA-CRASH-NYT (moved on Sunday, May 9)
</P>
<P>
   A New York Times News Service article sent on Sunday, May 9,
about a bus accident in New Orleans referred incorrectly in some
copies to the number of people killed in a 1976 accident in Yuba
City, Calif. That crash, the worst in the nation's history, killed
29, not 53.
</P>
